<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>救生艇新闻：博客——保护人类</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 04 Mar 2026 12:33:20 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>“AlphaFold 4”——科学家们对 DeepMind 药物衍生产品的独家新人工智能感到惊叹</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/an-alphafold-4-scientists-marvel-at-deepmind-drug-spin-offs-exclusive-new-ai</link><description>Isomorphic Labs 开发了一种药物-蛋白质相互作用模型，超越了该领域之前的技术。然而该模型是专有的，因此没有人知道它是如何设计和训练的以及为什么它效果如此之好！ &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/an-alphafold-4-scientists-marvel-at-deepmind-drug-spin-offs-exclusive-new-ai2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Mar 2026 12:33:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/an-alphafold-4-scientists-marvel-at-deepmind-drug-spin-offs-exclusive-new-ai</guid></item><item><title>DHL-11，一种从 Munronia henryi 中分离的新型 prieurianin 型柠檬苦素，靶向 IMPDH2 抑制三阴性乳腺癌</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/dhl-11-a-novel-prieurianin-type-limonoid-isolated-from-munronia-henryi-targeting-impdh2-to-inhibit-triple-negative-breast-cancer</link><description>乳腺癌被一种植物化合物摧毁。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/dhl-11-a-novel-prieurianin-type-limonoid-isolated-from-munronia-henryi-targeting-impdh2-to-inhibit-triple-negative-breast-cancer2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Mar 2026 12:18:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/dhl-11-a-novel-prieurianin-type-limonoid-isolated-from-munronia-henryi-targeting-impdh2-to-inhibit-triple-negative-breast-cancer</guid></item><item><title>探索原子终结的地方</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/the-quest-to-understand-where-atoms-end</link><description>范德华和共价半径等原子尺寸测量是化学的核心，但它们是否基于现实？&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/the-quest-to-understand-where-atoms-end2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Mar 2026 12:03:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/the-quest-to-understand-where-atoms-end</guid></item><item><title>大脑中的微小血液：数量和位置与痴呆症有关</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/tiny-blood-smidges-in-the-brain-amount-and-location-tied-to-dementia</link><description>倍性和神经元大小影响爪蟾神经系统的发育和功能。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/tiny-blood-smidges-in-the-brain-amount-and-location-tied-to-dementia2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Mar 2026 11:48:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/tiny-blood-smidges-in-the-brain-amount-and-location-tied-to-dementia</guid></item><item><title>非体外循环 CABG 的短期结果优于体外循环 CABG</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/off-pump-beats-on-pump-cabg-in-short-term-outcomes</link><description>与体外循环冠状动脉旁路移植术相比，非体外循环冠状动脉旁路移植术的围手术期发病率和死亡率降低，但长期生存率趋于平衡。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/off-pump-beats-on-pump-cabg-in-short-term-outcomes.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Mar 2026 11:33:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/off-pump-beats-on-pump-cabg-in-short-term-outcomes</guid></item><item><title>结直肠癌的质子治疗</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/proton-therapy-for-colorectal-cancer</link><description>自从 1954 年加州大学伯克利分校首次进行质子束疗法 (PBT) 治疗以来，PBT 在全球范围内的使用迅速增加。&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Mar 2026 11:18:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/proton-therapy-for-colorectal-cancer</guid></item><item><title>可注射的“卫星肝脏”可以提供肝移植的替代方案</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/injectable-satellite-livers-could-offer-an-alternative-to-liver-transplantation</link><description>超过 10,000 名患有慢性肝病的美国人正在等待肝移植，但没有足够的捐赠器官供所有这些患者使用。此外，许多肝衰竭患者如果健康状况不足以耐受手术，则不符合移植资格。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/injectable-satellite-livers-could-offer-an-alternative-to-liver-transplantation.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Mar 2026 11:03:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/injectable-satellite-livers-could-offer-an-alternative-to-liver-transplantation</guid></item><item><title>基于 2D 细胞模型和体外评估揭示红蔷薇叶提取物作为生物功能成分的生物特性</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/unveiling-the-biological-properties-of-rosa-rubiginosa-l-leaf-extract-as-a-bio-functional-ingredient-based-on-2d-cell-based-models-and-in-vitro-assessments</link><description>天然成分长期以来一直被用来增强人类健康。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/unveiling-the-biological-properties-of-rosa-rubiginosa-l-leaf-extract-as-a-bio-functional-ingredient-based-on-2d-cell-based-models-and-in-vitro-assessments2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Mar 2026 10:48:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/unveiling-the-biological-properties-of-rosa-rubiginosa-l-leaf-extract-as-a-bio-functional-ingredient-based-on-2d-cell-based-models-and-in-vitro-assessments</guid></item><item><title>缩小研究和患者护理之间的差距</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/closing-the-gap-between-research-and-patient-care</link><description>随着斯坦福大学医学院研究人员在新药、诊断和医疗设备方面取得进展。&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/closing-the-gap-between-research-and-patient-care.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Mar 2026 10:33:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/closing-the-gap-between-research-and-patient-care</guid></item><item><title>隔离尺寸对电子的影响</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/isolating-the-effect-of-dimensions-on-electrons</link><description>一种新的层状材料使研究人员能够记录当材料从 3D 变为 2D 时金属电子行为的巨大变化。&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/isolating-the-effect-of-dimensions-on-electrons2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Mar 2026 10:18:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/isolating-the-effect-of-dimensions-on-electrons</guid></item></channel></rss>